      <title>卡拉奇机场外发生严重爆炸，至少八人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-06/urgent-a-massive-blast-outside-karachi-airport-in-pakistan-injures-at-least-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡拉奇，巴基斯坦（美联社）——官员称，周日，巴基斯坦卡拉奇机场外发生严重爆炸，造成 2 人死亡，至少 8 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-06/urgent-a-massive-blast-outside-karachi-airport-in-pakistan-injures-at-least-4</guid>
