    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯表示，美国将继续向以色列施压，要求其实现加沙停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/kamala-harris-says-us-will-keep-pressuring-israel-for-gaza-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯表示，她不会停止向以色列施压，要求其结束在中东的军事行动，并强调在冲突持续一年之际，美国仍然在该地区发挥着关键作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/kamala-harris-says-us-will-keep-pressuring-israel-for-gaza-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 16:51:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院议长称国会可以等待海伦灾后恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/house-speaker-says-congress-can-wait-for-hurricane-damage-needs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，飓风海伦造成的破坏不需要国会立即采取行动增加联邦救灾资金，因为评估损失需要时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/house-speaker-says-congress-can-wait-for-hurricane-damage-needs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 14:52:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《图片报》称大众首席执行官认为中国可能采取报复性关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/vw-ceo-sees-threat-of-retaliatory-tariffs-from-china-bild-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《星期日图片报》报道，大众汽车集团首席执行官奥利弗·布鲁姆 (Oliver Blume) 希望找到针对中国电动汽车关税的替代解决方案，因为他准备应对北京方面可能采取的报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/vw-ceo-sees-threat-of-retaliatory-tariffs-from-china-bild-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 13:30:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的高级助手起诉格雷辞职，对英国首相造成新的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/starmer-s-top-aide-sue-gray-quits-in-fresh-blow-to-uk-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党赢得英国大选仅三个月后，基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的最资深顾问就辞职了，这对首相来说是一个重大打击，因为此前数周，他的内部争斗以及对他的政治行动日益增长的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/starmer-s-top-aide-sue-gray-quits-in-fresh-blow-to-uk-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>10 月 7 日里程碑前以色列加强对加沙和黎巴嫩的军事行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/israel-ramps-up-gaza-lebanon-operations-before-oct-7-milestone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 10 月 7 日哈马斯发动致命袭击一周年纪念日的前一天，以色列陷入了一场没有明确结束的多线战争，他们派军队回到加沙北部，并继续在黎巴嫩发动猛烈的空袭和有限的地面机动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/israel-ramps-up-gaza-lebanon-operations-before-oct-7-milestone</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选接近尾声 石油大亨成为特朗普主要现金来源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/oil-moguls-emerge-as-key-cash-source-for-trump-as-race-nears-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油业巨头纷纷慷慨解囊，支持共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普连任总统，他们已成为特朗普越来越重要的资金来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/oil-moguls-emerge-as-key-cash-source-for-trump-as-race-nears-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《纽约太阳报》所有者接近以 5.5 亿英镑收购《每日电讯报》：FT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/new-york-sun-owner-nears-550-million-deal-for-telegraph-ft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国《金融时报》报道，纽约《太阳报》的所有者即将以超过 5.5 亿英镑（7.22 亿美元）的价格收购英国《每日电讯报》。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/new-york-sun-owner-nears-550-million-deal-for-telegraph-ft</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 11:08:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和沃尔兹以“叫她爸爸”开启为期一周的媒体宣传攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/harris-walz-kick-off-week-long-media-blitz-with-call-her-daddy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯本周开始通过电视和播客节目进行媒体宣传，包括参加《Call Her Daddy》和《斯蒂芬·科尔伯特深夜秀》，试图在选举前吸引关键选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/harris-walz-kick-off-week-long-media-blitz-with-call-her-daddy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击加沙清真寺致 19 人死亡；对贝鲁特的轰炸加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-06/urgent-apparent-israeli-airstrike-on-mosque-in-central-gaza-kills-at-least-18-people</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代尔巴拉，加沙地带（美联社） — 以色列周日加强了对加沙北部和黎巴嫩南部的轰炸，与该地区与伊朗结盟的激进组织的战争不断扩大，而巴勒斯坦官员表示，对一座清真寺的袭击造成至少 19 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-06/urgent-apparent-israeli-airstrike-on-mosque-in-central-gaza-kills-at-least-18-people</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 04:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
